💰 PERSONAL EXPENSE TRACKER

A responsive and user-friendly Expense Tracker built with React.js and Tailwind CSS that helps you manage and visualize your daily spending easily.

Users can add, edit, and delete expenses, assign them to categories like 🛍️ Shopping, 🍔 Food, ✈️ Travel, 💡 Bills, etc., and view insightful summaries for income 💵, expenses 📉, and balance 📊.

🚀 Features

📅 Add / Edit / Delete expense records

🧾 Category-wise filtering (Food, Travel, Bills, etc.)

📈 Summary cards for total Income, Expenses, and Balance

🎨 Fully responsive UI built with Tailwind CSS

⚡ Fast & Dynamic frontend using React.js

💾 Data persistence using local storage / backend (future upgrade)

🛠️ Tech Stack
Technology	Purpose
React.js	Frontend framework
Tailwind CSS	Styling & layout
PostCSS	CSS processing
JavaScript (ES6+)	Logic and interactivity
npm	Dependency management
